        <TR>O Goddess, who could be able to talk about the characteristics of the soul?
                 There is no such thing as the form or colour of the soul or its location.</TR>

<TEXT> vyāpi sarvagataṃ sūkṣmaṃ sarvam{ }āśritya tiṣṭhati|</TEXT>
